  <body>
    <section id="requirements">
      <title>Requirements</title>
      <p>
        The Eclim plugins for vim require vim 7.  At the time of this writing,
        vim 7 is still alpha, but I have yet to encounter any major issues with
        it.  For information on obtaining and installing vim 7 please see the
        <a href="../install/index.html#vim_plugin">installation docs</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="configuration">
      <title>Configuration</title>
      <p>
        Currently there is only a couple global configuration settings
        available.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>g:EclimDebug</strong> (Default: 0)<br/>
          Setting this variable to 1 will turn on some simple debugging.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>g:EclimEchoHighlight</strong> (Default: "Statement")<br/>
          This determines which highlight group will be used for informative
          messages.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="java">
      <title>Java Source Editing</title>
      <p>
        Currently the vim integration with Eclipse consists of the following
